       <HR>
       <FONT size="+1"> Active compounds for use in the treatment of tumors
</FONT><BR>
       <BR><CENTER><b>Abstract</b></CENTER>
       <p>Antitumor compositions and methods in which a cancerostatic agent and an
     effective amount of (+)<B><I>-verapamil,</I></B> (+)-gallopamil, (+)-devapamil and/or
     (+)-emopamil which reinforce the antitumor action of the cancerostatic
     agent are administered to a patient either together or in sequence.
</p>
